# frontend-vendor provenance

This directory vendors a snapshot of the Odysseus SPA base (see
frontend-vendor/THIRD-PARTY.md for upstream project/license/source), modified
in place by workspace-repo commits since. It is NOT a pristine upstream
checkout — see "upstream revision" below.

